dct_description_sm: Includes on verso: tourist information, map of chief roads into and out of Paris, map of neighborhoods, and key to bus routes. Important building are shown pictorially. "Reproduction, même partielle, formellement interdite."
dct_creator_sm: France. Ministère des travaux publics, des transports et du tourisme
dct_publisher_sm: Paris : Ministère des travaux publics, des transports et du tourisme, 1961.
